{"tid":1310229,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【反修例】連儂牆「遍地開花」的風景：香港人加油！【圖輯】","createTime":"2019-07-12T14:41:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T15:10:44.000Z","uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ba7621d7150a0f057a135d8b0b82bcefcee847d4","tid":1310229,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:41:24.000Z","msg":"反修例行動遍地開花，各區均有市民設立連儂牆，一片Memo一片牆，承載不少人「反修例」市民的一片初心。雖然遭受多次摧殘，亦引發不少衝突事件，但牆和心依舊屹立。<br />\n<br />\n不少市民在連儂牆上寫上鼓勵字句：「香港人加油！」、「一個都不能少！珍惜生命」、「We walk hand in hand」；亦有市民為特首林鄭月娥製作「成績表」，批評施政；更有網民「抽水」，在牆上放下一元，並寫上「1蚊跟你機排隻揪」。TOPick攝影記者走訪多區連儂牆，把市民的心聲一一記下。<br />\nSource：<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2399122/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2399122%2F&d=f11PFKDsvG%2B7MRfNo%2B80BRd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=068b89fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2399122/</a>"},{"pid":"509f309a37d88a89de964391b38b3828a18c0714","tid":1310229,"uid":52090,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:42:17.000Z","msg":"試著說<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n<br />\n不割蓆，不分裂"},{"pid":"2e6936d445b154e4c54a2f62ab2e765cf1a573df","tid":1310229,"uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:43:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kp9QR3x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKp9QR3x.jpg&h=04932a76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 大埔「連儂隧道」上，市民以Memo紙砌出「加油」字樣。（張永康攝）<br />\n<strong><ins>將軍澳</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7dkTPQk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7dkTPQk.jpg&h=95f4e354&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<ins>▲ 有市民在連儂牆上拼湊區旗。（張永康攝）</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m3cSkXd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm3cSkXd.jpg&h=de967d3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<ins>▲ 將軍澳的連儂場寫滿「反修例」的訴求。（張永康攝）</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BOCSkXk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBOCSkXk.jpg&h=a439bd3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<ins>▲ 有市民在連儂牆上畫上網絡新興的Pepe The Frog（張永康攝）</ins>"},{"pid":"8e8b5a7b90b94621a5a43faf1a3b8afd76b1c81d","tid":1310229,"uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:44:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>九龍灣</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UybjLpj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUybjLpj.jpg&h=886bc3e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<ins>▲ 九龍灣連儂牆，有人寫上「We walk hand in hand」，勉勵同路人。（張永康攝）</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tPQ1ehM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtPQ1ehM.jpg&h=832006fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<ins>▲ 有市民表示：「條隊好長、幾時到我」；又有人抽水指「1蚊跟機」，更貼上一元硬幣。（張永康攝）</ins>"},{"pid":"9ca8aa3a86cd17d58e9c4978b2f10a0aa92fa831","tid":1310229,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:45:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>彩虹</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JVsrqpG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJVsrqpG.jpg&h=50b52faf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<ins>▲ 有市民貼上「壽終正寢」字句，諷刺林鄭月娥不願意撤回《逃犯條例》。（張永康攝）</ins>"},{"pid":"3aba901ee7d334932399faa910977fc214723cdd","tid":1310229,"uid":212626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:46:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>長沙灣</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vWD2JbC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvWD2JbC.jpg&h=2c96f815&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><ins>▲ 長沙灣港鐵站外的連儂牆，寫上「你撕一張，我貼一牆」的標語。（張永康攝）</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JF3ezio.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJF3ezio.jpg&h=810c99f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><ins>▲ 長沙灣街坊熱烈參與建造連儂牆。（張永康攝）</ins></strong>"},{"pid":"dbc8c7ee24a75ad475e41ec57f8adb7009507e91","tid":1310229,"uid":27664,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"c